**__Economy__**.**/crypto buy**: Action to buy a crypto of your wish
**__Economy__**.**/crypto sell**: Action to sell a crypto that you own
**__Economy__**.**/mine**: Mine command that claims nothing, BPPCs or a random cryptocurrency
**__Economy__**.**/help_info**: Can give some advice about sections on /crypto list image

**__/seemore commands__**.**intervals**: Enable/disable more time intervals in /crypto symbol
